==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Frutage
<hw>Frut"age</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf.
<er>Fruitage</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A picture of fruit;
decoration by representation of fruit.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The cornices consist of <qex>frutages</qex> and festoons.</q>
<rj><qau>Evelyn.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A confection of fruit.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Nares.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Frutescent</ent>⟦br⟧
